				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Triggers if Wyll broke his pact with Mizora and then went to the Iron Throne to save Ravengard. As soon as players free Ravengard and move him out of his cell to the middle of the room, this dialog will play."
				},
