				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Mizora appears and commands Ravengard to fall to his knees, bound by her infernal charms. She then mentions  that she will summono some spiders as well and leaves.\r\n\r\nIf players somehow cured the Infernal charms from Ravengard, she has an alternative branch where she only summons the spiders."
